 the internal pressures of clouds in several galaxies\nscales with the external pressure exerted on the clouds by the ambient ISM:\nP_int ~ P_ext^{0.75+/-0.05}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Jan 2005 21:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Jan 2005 21:10:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-30"}
